            <h1>THE RHYTHM OF VANKALAI <br> <span>Where Wings Carve Stories</span></h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Intro -->
        <div class="mainpara">
            <p>
                <em>The Rhythm of Vankalai</em> is a poetic short documentary capturing
                the tranquil beauty of birdlife in the Vankalai Lagoon, Mannar —
                a Ramsar Wetland of International Importance. Against still waters
                and golden morning light, the lagoon’s winged residents move in harmony,
                creating a timeless dance of nature. This sanctuary is home to both
                resident and migratory birds, offering a glimpse into a world where
                peace still lingers.
            </p>
        </div>

